Hi Brittany, this can be edited in the template directly so you have a default text. The way to do so is a piece of code:
```{% if QUOTE_PROPS.hs_terms|length &lt; 1 %}
Default text
{% elif QUOTE_PROPS.hs_terms|length &gt; 0 %}
{{ QUOTE_PROPS.hs_terms }}
{% endif %}```
This way it will display "Default text" when empty and the actual text if the suer adds one in the quote creation flow.
